---
const personalImageAlt = "Kevin Simorangkir";
const defaultImage = "/KVNS.png";
---

<article
  class="kvns-profile flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 md:flex-row transition-all duration-700 ease-in-out"
>
  <!-- ðŸ§© Text -->
  <div
    class="[&>p]:mb-6 [&>p>strong]:text-[var(--brand-500)]
           dark:[&>p>strong]:text-[var(--brand-400)]
           [&>p>strong]:font-semibold
           leading-relaxed order-2 md:order-1 max-w-xl text-justify font-inter tracking-wide"
  >
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed">
      My name is <strong>Kevin Simorangkir</strong>, and I began learning
      programming in high school, driven by my passion for building digital
      experiencesâ€”from computer games to mobile applications. Iâ€™ve contributed
      to communities and companies, creating projects such as
      <strong>REFORA ITERA, Harvesty, SIPAD,</strong> and other design systems.
    </p>

    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed">
      These include
      <strong
        >Telkom Witel Lampung, Telkom Indonesia, Yayasan Media Selaras,</strong
      >
      and <strong>Baparekraf Digital Talent</strong>. Each journey has deepened
      my curiosity and strengthened my drive to learn, grow, and innovate.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- ðŸ§© Profile Image -->
  <div class="relative order-1 md:order-2 group">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr
             from-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_60%_40%_/_0.18)] via-transparent to-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_60%_40%_/_0.06)]
             dark:from-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_40%_22%_/_0.18)] dark:to-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_40%_22%_/_0.10)]
             rounded-3xl blur-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100
             transition-opacity duration-700"
    >
    </div>

    <img
      width="260"
      height="260"
      src={defaultImage}
      alt={personalImageAlt}
      class="object-cover aspect-square rounded-3xl
             p-2 w-64 h-64 shadow-xl shadow-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_60%_20%_/_0.25)]
             dark:shadow-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_60%_20%_/_0.18)]
             bg-gradient-to-br from-white/70 to-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_60%_40%_/_0.10)]
             dark:from-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_24%_13%_/_0.40)] dark:to-black/40
             ring-2 ring-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_60%_40%_/_0.30)] dark:ring-[hsl(var(--brand-h)_60%_40%_/_0.22)]
             transition-all duration-700 ease-in-out
             group-hover:scale-[1.01] hover:brightness-[1.02]"
      style="object-position: 50% 50%"
    />
  </div>
</article>

<style>
  .kvns-profile {
    --brand-h: 192;
    --brand-s: 70%;
    --brand-l: 42%;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .kvns-profile {
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
    .kvns-profile img {
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
    }
  }
</style>
